OL,3,CReform UK leader denies struggling for
OL,4,Ccandidates amid 'cold calling' claims
OL,6,FNigel Farage has denied claims that
OL,7,FReform UK has struggled to find
OL,8,Felection candidates, after reports the
OL,9,Fparty had been contacting members of
OL,10,Frival parties and asking them to stand.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives said some of their
OL,13,Fmembers, as well as Liberal Democrats,
OL,14,Fhad been approached ahead of the
OL,15,Fcandidate deadline on Thursday.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Farage
OL,18,Frejected suggestions Reform UK had
OL,19,Fbeen "cold calling" potential
OL,20,Fcandidates.
OL,26,@{D@FOU{D@SO]
