OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1775667952
OL,3,CReform UK leader denies struggling for
OL,4,Ccandidates amid 'cold calling' claims
OL,6,FHe said: "No, cold calling would be
OL,7,Fvery, very fruitless, wouldn't it?
OL,9,F"Have we called paid-up members of the
OL,10,Fparty to see if they want to get
OL,11,Fengaged? Yes, but of course, every
OL,12,Fparty does that.
OL,14,F"The Labour Party has actually been
OL,15,Fadvertising online for candidates in
OL,16,Fthe North East of England.
OL,18,F"I can promise you right now there'll
OL,19,Fbe a full slate of candidates across
OL,20,Fthe West Midlands."
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
