OL,3,CReform UK leader denies struggling for
OL,4,Ccandidates amid 'cold calling' claims
OL,6,FFarage added that all parties were
OL,7,Funder pressure to meet the nomination
OL,8,Fdeadline.
OL,10,F"I think you'll find across the whole
OL,11,Fof the country, with over 5,000
OL,12,Fcandidates, if you include Scotland
OL,13,Fand Wales, that all parties are
OL,14,Frunning very, very fast.
OL,16,F"The deadline is 11:00am on the ninth,
OL,17,Fso in two days' time everyone's got to
OL,18,Fstruggle on."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
