CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1775667952
OL,3,CReform UK leader denies struggling for
OL,4,Ccandidates amid 'cold calling' claims
OL,6,FHe also repeated his pledge that
OL,7,FReform UK would field a full slate of
OL,8,Fcandidates in the West Midlands.
OL,10,FBirmingham's Liberal Democrat leader
OL,11,Fsaid he hadn't heard any reports of
OL,12,Fits councillors or candidates being
OL,13,Fapproached by Reform UK.
OL,15,FFarage was speaking in Bedworth in
OL,16,FWarwickshire, where he appeared
OL,17,Falongside the mother of hotel worker
OL,18,FRhiannon Whyte, who was murdered in
OL,19,FWalsall in 2024 by a Sudanese asylum
OL,20,Fseeker.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
