CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1775667952
OL,3,CReform UK leader denies struggling for
OL,4,Ccandidates amid 'cold calling' claims
OL,6,FShe claimed more people would be
OL,7,Fmurdered and raped in the UK if small
OL,8,Fboat crossings continue.
OL,10,FFarage also addressed the prospect of
OL,11,Fa coalition with the Conservatives.
OL,13,FLast week, Kemi Badenoch said she
OL,14,Fwould not block Conservatives from
OL,15,Fjoining a local coalition with Reform
OL,16,FUK in Birmingham.
OL,18,FFarage said: "It's not going to be
OL,19,Fnecessary. I'm pretty confident
OL,20,Fbecause the left is completely split."
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@fO]
